      "content": "it's not just a mistake though. it's fundamental. everything i've said, everything i've published... it's all built on a void. i feel like a ghost inhabiting a life that was meant for someone else. how am i supposed to just \"move forward\" when the person who was supposed to be doing this work doesn't actually exist? the version of me that mattered is dead.",
